STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Tatrone R. WATERS, Defendant-Respondent. C-677 September Term 2017
080229 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 9, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002815-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
